column4: New growth cannot exist without first the destruction of the old.
What the airbenders had lacked in skill and power they made up for in numbers.
A powerful gust of wind washes over the surprised Chin and strips him of all his clothes except for his underwear.
An Avatar-level airbender can create massive tornadoes and hurricanes at will.
Jennamite otherwise known as creeping crystal grows at remarkably fast speeds when it comes into contact with organic matter.
With proper timing an earthbender can bind an opponent's arms with triangle-shaped slabs.
A master earthbender can launch shrapnel-like fragments of earth with great speed.
An earthbender can cause many rocks of a multitude of sizes to rain down on their opponent.
A fight for one's honor and is won only when one opponent burns the other.
Their fire was beautiful. I saw so many colors colors I've never imagined.
Iroh was the last outsider to face the masters. They deemed him worthy and passed the secret onto him as well.
From our airships we will rain fire over their lands a fire that will destroy everything; and out of the ashes a new world will be born.
They're called fire lilies. They only bloom a few weeks a year. And like all plants and all living things they're filled with water.
It its wrath the Ocean Spirit La laid waste to the Fire Nation's armies.
When he took my bending the sensation was somehow familiar. I later recognized it as my brother's bloodbending grip.
The Great Serpent is trapped caught in the maelstrom.
